These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, tea
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, van
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, journalist
3 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, fish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, gospel, hip-hop
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, spanish
 1. the journalist is in an odd position##4
 2. the person drinking juice is in the middle##1
 3. the spanish is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 4. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the fan gospel##3
 5. the owner of the hamster is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 6. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
 8. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the fan hip-hop##5
 9. the entrepreneur is between the fan funk and the spanish##2
10. the chinese is on the left of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | tea        | juice        | lemonade    |
| Hobby         | snowmobile    | van       | bike      |
| Job           | journalist | entrepreneur | electrician |
| Movie-Genre   | hamster     | lizard   | fish |
| Music-Genre   | funk       | hip-hop      | gospel      |
| Nationality   | canadian   | chinese      | spanish     |

