 8. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
 9. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
10. the colonial house is between the person driving the quad-bike and the gothic-revival house##2
11. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
12. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5

