 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | fanta          | almond-milk |
| Food          | card-games        | reading     | woodworking |
| Job           | lawyer        | police-officer | scientist   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime         | drama          | time-travel |
| Sport         | lacrosse      | basketball     | water-polo  |
| Transport     | whist       | bridge            | scrabble       |

