There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, polish, spanish
3 different pets are kept: dog, rat, snake
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, lilac, chestnut
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, singing, chess
 1. the polish is not the person drinking 7up##6
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who likes lilac##2
 3. the spanish is not the owner of the dog##6
 4. the engineer is not the person who's hobby is singing##6
 5. the engineer is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
 6. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is the spanish##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who likes lilac##1
 9. the mexican is on the right of the firefighter##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
11. the person who's hobby is chess is not the person who likes chestnut##6
12. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the firefighter##1

